metadata.name: MATE HOUSE
metadata.description:
After the battle, MATE are resting for the first time in a while.

We're looking at a panoramic view of the city where the MATEs live. Mate is a star in this city. Like the popularity of KPOP celebrities, they are always receiving hot attention in the city. Because they fight the Judgement-Dragon to protect the city. And the evolved new race is subject to fear and attention.
